    <task id="LOCAL-00006" summary="Implement comprehensive document management features, cloud integrations, and UI/UX enhancements.&#10;&#10;### Core Features &amp; Enhancements&#10;*   **Document Management**:&#10;    *   Implement a **Templates Library** with 6 professional LaTeX templates (Article, Beamer, Report, etc.).&#10;    *   Fix tab title extraction using `ContentResolver` for accurate filenames across all URI types.&#10;    *   Add **Undo/Redo** functionality with a debounced state stack.&#10;    *   Implement **Find &amp; Replace** with match counting and navigation.&#10;    *   Add a **Symbol Toolbar** for quick insertion of LaTeX commands and special characters.&#10;    *   Implement **Auto-save** with configurable intervals and a **Line Number View**.&#10;&#10;### Cloud &amp; Connectivity&#10;*   **GitHub Integration**: Add OAuth2 flow for connecting accounts and storing encrypted access tokens.&#10;*   **Google Drive Integration**: Implement Google Sign-In with `drive.file` scope for cloud storage access.&#10;*   **Security**: Add `EncryptedSharedPreferences` via `CloudPrefs` for secure token storage.&#10;&#10;### UI/UX Improvements&#10;*   **Recent Files**: Overhaul the recent files list with a rich card-based UI showing file paths and &quot;remove&quot; functionality.&#10;*   **Tabs**: Enhance `TabLayout` with dirty state indicators (unsaved changes), improved touch targets, and a &quot;New Tab&quot; button.&#10;*   **Menu**: Redesign the bottom sheet menu with categorized sections (File, Edit, View, Editor, Cloud) and theme switching (Light/Dark/System).&#10;*   **Editor**: Add pinch-to-zoom support, document statistics (word/char count), and &quot;Jump to Line&quot; functionality.&#10;&#10;### Technical &amp; Configuration&#10;*   **Refactoring**: Modularize `LatexHtml` into multiple files (`LatexHtmlParsing`, `LatexHtmlBlocks`, `LatexHtmlUtils`, etc.) for better maintainability.&#10;*   **Build System**: Add `BuildConfig` fields for API client IDs and update dependencies for Play Services Auth, OkHttp, and Security Crypto.&#10;*   **Resources**: Add numerous vector drawables for UI actions and update Material 3 theme configurations.&#10;*   **Documentation**: Add extensive guides for cloud setup, lint fixes, and implementation summaries.">
